                     <interp inst="t17191014-24-off121" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               receiving 550 dozen of Leather Soles for shoes value 150 l. 30 dozen Calve skins, from 
                     <persName id="t17191014-24-person80">
                        Mary 
                        Clarke 
                     <interp inst="t17191014-24-person80" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
