                  , Convicted last Sections for the same, by her pleading Guilty) the Goods of 
                     <persName id="t17191014-24-victim81" type="victimName">
                        George 
                        Laugthorse 
                     <interp inst="t17191014-24-victim81" type="surname" value="Laugthorse"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17191014-24-victim81" type="given" value="George"></interp>
